General.Name: Rapid Nutrition PLC
General.Description: Rapid Nutrition PLC, a natural healthcare company, develops and distributes a rage of science-based health and wellness products in the United Kingdom, Europe, North America, Australia, Asia, and internationally. The company offers organic and natural scientific-based health foods, including various high-protein shakes, organic superfoods, vegan powders, natural metabolism boosters, and high-protein bars under the SystemLS brand; and weight loss systems under the Leisa's Secret brand name. It also provides products that aids to relieve symptoms of colds and the flu under the Azurene brand name. Rapid Nutrition PLC was founded in 2001 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
General.Address: 124 City Road, London, United Kingdom, EC1V 2NX
